  "body": "When performing a fast sync the list of pending nodes only stores the node hash.  We also need to know the Location of the request (likely in unpacked form, one 4-bit section per byte) and the account for account trie storage requests.\n\nIt is expected this will touch classes in `org.hyperledger.besu.ethereum.eth.sync.worldstate` with the key functions being `org.hyperledger.besu.ethereum.eth.sync.worldstate.NodeDataRequest#serialize` and `org.hyperledger.besu.ethereum.eth.sync.worldstate.NodeDataRequest#deserialize`.\n\nThese two values will need to be used to determine the keys for the bonsai world state downloader, so once that branch is merged these can be wired into that task.",
